Summary: 2 golden square shape hovering over (it seemed) delamare river
divs: Sighting Detailsdriving along delaware river going to my cousins house and i just happened to look towards the river and seen 2 golden square shape objects (floating,hoavering) side by side. i brought it to my cousins attention and he pulled over. then got out of the car and stared in augh for about 10 mins. then we got back in the car and drove off and i couldn't keep my eyes off the objects. as we drove farther i lost vision of the objects.we got to my cousins house and tried to figure out what we saw and we summed it up to it had to of been ufo's.
